convo_1: [""A: Let's go get lunch!"", 'B: Where do you want to go?', ""A: Let's try that new restaurant down the street.""]"

convo_1: ['A: Do you want to meet up for lunch?', 'B: Sure, where are we going?', 'A: It depends. Are you a picky eater?']"

convo_1: ['A: Can I check in here at the curb?', 'B: Sure! Do you have any bags you need to check in?', 'A: I have one suitcase.']"

convo_4: [""A: Do you know John's address?"", ""B: No, I don't. Why do you need it?"", ""A: I want to invite his son to my daughter's party.""]"

convo_1: ['A: I love peanuts.', 'B: Me, too. I love them roasted and salted.', 'A: I love boiled peanuts.']"

convo_1: ['A: This line is so long!', ""B: We've been waiting for almost an hour!"", 'A: I guess they do a really thorough check.']"

convo_1: ['A: Everything is going wrong today.', 'B: Well, at least the weather is nice.', 'A: Oh, yeah. Imagine if it had rained like they said it would.']"

convo_1: ['A: Have you ever heard of poison ivy?', ""B: Isn't that a super villain?"", ""A: I wouldn't know. Tell me more.""]"
